    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chips are in the oven, combine your <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>hoisin sauce</strong>, <strong>tomato ketchup</strong> and <strong>ginger & garlic paste </strong>with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>sugar</strong> in a bowl – this is your <strong>Mongolian-style BBQ marinade</strong></p>",
