            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>beef mince</strong> and <strong>half</strong> your <strong>Mongolian-style BBQ marinade</strong> in a bowl</p><p>Give everything a good mix up until thoroughly combined (clean hands is the best way!)</p><p>Divide and shape them into 1 patty per person – these are your <strong>Mongolian-style BBQ patty[ies]</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
