      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 150ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[175ml]</span> [200ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> to the <strong>remaining marinade</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>Mongolian-style BBQ sauce</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>carrot, mooli & pink cabbage slaw mix </strong>with your <strong>rice vinegar</strong> and 1/2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [1 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>– this is your<strong> quick-pickled mooli slaw</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
