            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1694089946691-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After 5 min, decrease the heat to medium-high and turn the patty[ies] over, then add the <strong>Mongolian-style BBQ sauce</strong> to the pan</p><p>Reserve the bowl</p><p>Cook for 5 min further, spooning the sauce over the patty[ies] until thickened to a gravy-like consistency and the beef is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1694089950612-x200.jpg",
