            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>mayo</strong> and <strong>sriracha </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) in the reserved bowl – this is your <strong>sriracha mayo</strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>brioche bun[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Remove the tray[s] with the chips from the oven and add the <strong>brioche halves</strong>, cut side up, then return the tray to the oven for 3-4 min or until warmed through</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1694089953501-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
