          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1694089953501-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To assemble your burger, top each <strong>brioche</strong> <strong>base </strong>with the <strong>sriracha mayo</strong>, a handful of<strong> quick-pickled mooli slaw </strong>and a <strong>Mongolian-style BBQ beef patty</strong>, drizzle over a little <strong>Mongolian-style BBQ sauce</strong> and top with a <strong>brioche lid</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>remaining quick-pickled Mooli slaw</strong> and <strong>chips</strong> to the side with any <strong>remaining Mongolian-style BBQ sauce</strong> to a small pot and serve to the side for dipping</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
